profile:
Drain Right Now strives to be the best drain cleaning and plumbing service provider. We are courteous, competent, and complete all work with honesty and integrity, and most of all we provide our customers with the best value and service for their hard earned dollar. 
 
We offer a wide variety of residential/commercial plumbing and drain services including drain cleaning, drain repairs of all types, fixture installations/repairs, sumps and sewage pumps, renovations and so much more!

 For all of our customers we always include a complimentary residential full home plumbing inspection to ensure the utmost care and service of your residential plumbing needs. All inspections include a full report for the homeowner and a flat rate price to complete each individual repair.

 
We service Barrie, Orillia, Gravenhurst, Bracebridge, Midland, Penetang, Penetanguishine, Wasaga Beach, Collingwood, Angus, Utopia, Midhurst, Alliston, Base Borden, New Lowell, Minesing, Anten Mills, Springwater, Phelpston, Elmvale, Tay Township, Tiny Township, Stayner, Creemore, Mansfield, Mulmur, Cookstown, Thornton, Bradford, Newmarket, Holland Landing, Queensville, Lefroy, Gilford, Churchhill, Bell Ewart, Innisfil, Alcona, Oro, Oro Station, Oro-Medonte, Hawekstone, Washago, Cumberland Beach, Rama, Ramara, Brechin, Lagoon City, Severn Bridge, Severn Falls, Port Severn, Baysville, Port Carling, Essa, Coldwater, Orr Lake, Moonstone, Dalrymple Lake
